description:
**During COVID 19 event** this property will not accept instant booking and bookings must be made for a minimum of 2 consecutive nights. The dorm will not be shared among separate parties.
Close to Port Arthur & 3 Capes Walks, our share house is set among tall trees by the edge of a bay. One shared, mixed, 4 bed dorm room & one double room share kitchen, lounge & bathroom. Free wifi.
Might have beds when none show - call or enquire

description:
Sunny place with modern kitchen and bathroom. Open plan living space with a heat pump.

There's 1 off-street parking if you have a car, there's a bus stop very close as well.

Only 15 minutes drive to the city and 10 minutes to MONA. 5 minutes drive to Moonah Centre with all kinds of restaurants, bars and supermarkets.

I also have a very friendly cat named Dollar, he would like you to pat and play with him.

description: Montacute Boutique Bunkhouse is a multi-award winning boutique hostel suitable for backpackers, groups of friends, couples and families. We are located in central Hobart in the historic village of Battery Point. We have double rooms, private bunkrooms and shared bunkrooms as well as shared facilities including a large kitchen, dining room, lounge room, balcony, deck, garden, coin laundry. FREE wifi, luggage storage, parking and BBQ.
